Output .vhs/write.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 800
Set Height 360
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Type "./bin/candyshell write --header 'Release notes:'"
Enter
Sleep 700ms
Type "## v1.0"
Enter
Type "First public release."
Enter
Type "- feature: cell-diff renderer"
Enter
Type "- fix: paginator wraparound"
Sleep 700ms
Ctrl+d
Sleep 800ms
